{"tid":2479340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方搗破懷疑開放派對房間　被捕負責人為警員","createTime":"2021-04-07T18:03:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T21:11:07.000Z","uid":227801,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"647443d6c76d2af9081cd0471461d13722cce2f0","tid":2479340,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T18:03:13.000Z","msg":"警方搗破懷疑開放派對房間　被捕負責人為警員<br />\n<br />\n警方根據線報，經深入調查後昨日突擊搜查觀塘道一個樓上單位，搗破一間懷疑正在開放的派對房間。警方在行動中拘捕一名26歲負責人，他是一名警員；另外單位內有5名男子，其中一名25歲男子亦是警員,，他們涉嫌違反限聚令。涉案懷疑是處所負責人的警員，涉嫌違反預防及控制疾病的業務及處所規例，獲准保釋候查，須於下月上旬向警方報到。警方表示，警隊非常重視人員操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍及姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n2021-04-08 01:24:38<br />\n<br />\n[url]https://ne<del><a href=\"http://ws.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1584660-202\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fws.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1584660-202&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYTH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=99ebef47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ws.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1584660-202</a></del>10408.htm[/url]"},{"pid":"28c8d573ee5a9760edc5e8e705f047e3cc2765fb","tid":2479340,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T18:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開名啦 分分鐘扮黃"},{"pid":"15a7b7f7a1ce93f8ec42495e4606c236c2e608dd","tid":2479340,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T18:04:56.000Z","msg":"秘撈有冇申報？"},{"pid":"deb7e9d65926e7427bd96ede318ea700adc97a74","tid":2479340,"uid":74303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T18:05:17.000Z","msg":"佢唔記得嗌「自己友」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616e071f40f65d8120548478f5e9d52dd9270bc8","tid":2479340,"uid":185492,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T18:06:38.000Z","msg":"屌，負責人唔係警員先係新聞麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e67d5b57be2ef6193c65aec19dbecc958186a418","tid":2479340,"u